desc: Doghouse Cafe is Melbourne's one-stop-shop for all your dogs needs. We specialise in making Premium Raw Dog Food Blends for your dog. Made fresh daily from premium whole-foods designed to promote the health and well-being of any adult dog, regardless of breed or age. We even make Dog Birthday Cakes! Delivery available*

layout.text: Why not celebrate your pups birthday at the cafe?! We can sort everything out for you - from a birthday cake to balloons & decorations, and party bags to take home for your furry guests! We can even sort out some party food for the humans!
